{"tid":914153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿嬌下月結婚】楊受成「嫁女」幫埋單 預告開40幾圍兼包辦酒水","createTime":"2018-11-24T04:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T10:42:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77197df427ee791e5f70d1c2eede0cecd2eb06e6","tid":914153,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"英皇老闆楊受成、洗米華周焯華、吳浩康同彭秀慧等，噚晚喺銅鑼灣出席《箭神&middot;第一戰》首映，洗米華未有接受訪問，佢一見到楊生就不停咬耳仔密密斟，佢哋一齊主持首映祝酒儀式，之後就齊齊入去睇戲。<br />\n提到近期好多英皇電影上映，楊受成話：「唔多，不過我哋自己出品嘅今個月就有4套戲拍緊，咁啱演員啲期都係11月。」講到公司最近簽咗毛舜筠同彭秀慧導演，楊生就話：「係呀，遲啲會開戲畀毛舜筠，傾緊度身訂造劇本畀佢。」<br />\n提到鍾欣潼（阿嬌）下月20號結婚，楊生就話好開心，問到係咪要阿嬌跪地斟茶？佢就話：「要斟茶，但唔使跪啦。」楊生答應負責包辦酒席、酒水，佢話：「唔知幾多圍，酒店嗰度最多40幾圍，應該都會擺晒。」不過楊生就話未知幾多錢埋單，笑言都有上限。問到會唔會上台致辭？佢就話：「唔講啦，咁老土，驚講講下我會喊。」至於會否催阿嬌快啲生仔？楊生話：「我點催到，我個仔都催唔到，順其自然啦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543031930_d93f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543031930_d93f.jpg&h=cbbadbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181124/58951951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58951951&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b0b250f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58951951&h=273fa271\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181124/58951951</a>"},{"pid":"3e456522c0923e4c4731067c40c3c11abeddd353","tid":914153,"uid":29070,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"幫佢吹埋"},{"pid":"d482a06f9561037b6b06c73f1bcabc5a7457e43d","tid":914153,"uid":37487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"有咩未睇過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a943ecf5e21ce73bbd5a75e2732e0b92c99e9ac6","tid":914153,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"咩姿勢都解鎖晒"},{"pid":"460a71de289ea1d5ffedaea3315063819f305fdf","tid":914153,"uid":46910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"係咪食過啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又出錢出力"},{"pid":"e4e5ae4fd19de521e06786509ad83c7cdabb007f","tid":914153,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460a71de289ea1d5ffedaea3315063819f305fdf","tid":914153,"uid":46910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"係咪食過啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又出錢出力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}